OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773867709
OL,3,CLyons accuses Sinn Fein of 'shirking
OL,4,Cresponsibilities' over heating oil
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FPoliticians have been urged to stop
OL,8,Fpoint scoring over who is responsible
OL,9,Ffor distributing a package of help for
OL,10,Fhome heating oil customers after the
OL,11,FPrime Minister announced #17million of
OL,12,Ffunding for the Executive.
OL,14,FFinance Minister John O'Dowd asked
OL,15,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons to
OL,16,Fcome up with proposals.
OL,26,@kD@Urr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
