FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773867709
OL,3,CLyons accuses Sinn Fein of 'shirking
OL,4,Cresponsibilities' over heating oil
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FHowever, Mr Lyons has accused Sinn
OL,8,FFein of "shirking their
OL,9,Fresponsibilities" saying energy policy
OL,10,Ffalls within the remit of Economy
OL,11,FMinister Caoimhe Archibald.
OL,13,FOn Monday, the Prime Minister
OL,14,Fannounced a #17million support package
OL,15,Fto support households struggling with
OL,16,Fthe rising cost of home heating oil,
OL,17,Fwith the Executive to decide how the
OL,18,Fmoney was allocated.
OL,20,FDUP Leader Gavin Robinson made it
OL,21,Fclear who he thought needed to step up.
OL,26,@kD@UrrpD@Brr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773867709
OL,3,CLyons accuses Sinn Fein of 'shirking
OL,4,Cresponsibilities' over heating oil
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"That's why I'm indicating not only a
OL,8,Fwillingness to work with the Economy
OL,9,FMinister, but a requirement for her to
OL,10,Fsharpen her pencil and get going with
OL,11,Fdiscussions about how best this
OL,12,FExecutive can target resource
OL,13,Feffectively to support those who need
OL,14,Fit most", he said.
OL,16,FFinance Minister John O'Dowd, who
OL,17,Fcontrols Northern Ireland's budgets,
OL,18,Fsaid he believed it was up to another
OL,19,FMinister formulate a plan.
OL,26,@kD@UrroD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773867709
OL,3,CLyons accuses Sinn Fein of 'shirking
OL,4,Cresponsibilities' over heating oil
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"I'll be writing to my colleague, the
OL,8,FMinister for Communities Gordon Lyons,
OL,9,Fasking him to bring forward proposals
OL,10,Fin relation to how this funding should
OL,11,Fbe best used in the time ahead and
OL,12,Fasking for proposals to be brought
OL,13,Fforward which allow this money to be
OL,14,Fspent quickly", he said.
OL,16,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons hit
OL,17,Fback.
OL,19,F""In my view, this is an issue for the
OL,20,FDepartment for the Economy. They have
OL,21,Fthe lead on energy policy.
OL,26,@kD@Urr{D@BOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773867709
OL,3,CLyons accuses Sinn Fein of 'shirking
OL,4,Cresponsibilities' over heating oil
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"When I was in that post in 2022, I
OL,8,Fmade sure that we got that support in
OL,9,Fplace - #600 for every household.
OL,11,F"Unfortunately, it seems that Sinn
OL,12,FFein are shirking their
OL,13,Fresponsibilities saying this is too
OL,14,Fdifficult for us, so we're going to
OL,15,Fpass this on to somebody else instead.
OL,17,F"What we should be doing is working
OL,18,Ftogether", he told reporters in
OL,19,FWashington on Monday night.
OL,26,@kD@UrroD@AOUsD@AOUtD@BrryD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
