CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773867709
OL,3,CLyons accuses Sinn Fein of 'shirking
OL,4,Cresponsibilities' over heating oil
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe Secretary of State has suggested
OL,8,Fthat an #81million discount to
OL,9,Felectricity bills and additional money
OL,10,Fin the budget could be repurposed for
OL,11,Fwider support.
OL,13,F"If the Executive adds them all
OL,14,Ftogether and chooses to apply those
OL,15,Fsums of money to help in particular
OL,16,Fpeople on low incomes who are
OL,17,Fdependent on heating oil then the sums
OL,18,Fof money being given to families would
OL,19,Fbe much bigger than that but it
OL,20,Fdepends on the choice that the
OL,21,FExecutive makes," he said.
OL,26,@kD@UrruD@AOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
