PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1773867709
OL,3,CLyons accuses Sinn Fein of 'shirking
OL,4,Cresponsibilities' over heating oil
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThose seeking help feel they are
OL,8,Fcaught in the middle.
OL,10,F"If they were going to give it out,
OL,11,FStormont would be better shutting
OL,12,Ftheir mouth about fighting with other
OL,13,Fparties and get it out to the people
OL,14,Finstead of arguing all the time trying
OL,15,Fto score points against one another.
OL,17,F"Get out the money. If they have to
OL,18,Fuse the Winter Fuel allowance to send
OL,19,Fthe money out that way if that's the
OL,20,Fquickest way of getting that out to
OL,21,Fpeople.
OL,26,@kD@UrryD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
