OL,3,CLyons accuses Sinn Fein of 'shirking
OL,4,Cresponsibilities' over heating oil
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"They need it now when it's cold", one
OL,8,Fmember of the public told UTV.
OL,10,FAround two-thirds of homes in Northern
OL,11,FIreland use home heating oil compared
OL,12,Fwith the UK average of just more than
OL,13,F5%.JThe exact number of people who
OL,14,Fwill get help is still to be decided.
